48261.title: 2 Broke Girls
48261.description: Wanneer Max en Caroline hun klanten verliezen aan de gekte rondom de 'cronut' (half croissant, half donut), verzinnen ze zelf ook een trend: cakefrietjes.

48262.title: 2 Broke Girls
48262.description: After Caroline buys hair extensions with her and Max's joint funds, Caroline feels guilty and splurges on a new bedding set for Max. But she gives the old set to charity, not realizing Max's old pillowcase has sentimental value for her, and the two go to extremes in search of Max's cherished pillowcase.

48368.title: 2 Broke Girls
48368.description: Max decides to apply to the Manhattan School of Pastry and bakes a tart for her entrance exam. Gilles Marini (Sex and the City, Switched at Birth, Brothers & Sisters) guest stars as Nicolas, the handsome French "master baker" who owns and teaches at the school. Mary Lynn Rajskub (24) guest stars as Bebe, a neurotic pastry chef who works at the front desk.
